==== ENTRY 3 ====
HEADWORD: Substrate
<hw>Sub*strate"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>substratus</ets>, p. p. of <ets>substrahere</ets>. See
<er>Substratum</er>.]</ety> <def>To strew or lay under anything.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The melted glass being supported by the <qex>substrated</qex>
sand.</q> <rj><qau>Boyle.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

